{"tid":1876593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(政治藝術) 美國: 拒讓台灣參與\"宗教自由聯盟\", 但亦呼籲中共立即停止脅迫台灣","createTime":"2020-02-12T13:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T00:30:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9874860373d134b803e0f8cf1d4c79d976937159","tid":1876593,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"美國人的政治藝術: 如何在(口講)遵守&quot;一個中國&quot;原則下, 守護台灣.<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院最近發起的「宗教自由聯盟」決定排除台灣，美國國務院亦婉拒台灣副總統賴清德出席美國國務卿的晚宴. <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3065245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3065245&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=eb9f29dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3065245&h=59775762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3065245</a><br />\n<br />\n但同時間, 美國國務院亦公開呼籲中共立即停止脅迫台灣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?NewsID=688249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D688249&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=168bff5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D688249&h=7208f440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?NewsID=688249</a><br />\n<em>針對近日中國派遣軍機武力威脅臺灣一事，美國務院發言人回應媒體詢問時，呼籲北京應立即停止脅迫行徑，與臺灣民選政府恢復對話，並對任何企圖以非和平方式決定臺灣未來的作法表達嚴正關切。對此，外交部發言人歐江安今（12）日回應表示誠摯感謝，並強調將持續深化與美國合作關係。</em>"},{"pid":"e1a7c60a54ef5ed604525160f5cedf2cd0d6b367","tid":1876593,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"美國又示範政治藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74593dd942a3d93c2e46bd90c511391bfda6305","tid":1876593,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:22:50